<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3926867>
    dc:description "Figs 31–35. — 31–32. Ophryocotlyoides dasi Tandan & Singh, 1964. 31. Scolex with double crown of hooks, spinuous pseudoproboscis and armed suckers margins. 32. Mature proglottis, ventral view. — 33–35. Variolepis cf. bilharzii (Krabbe, 1869). 33. Scolex. 34. Rostellar hooks. 35. Mature proglottis. Scale bars: 31, 33 = 50 µm; 32 = 250 µm; 34 = 20 µm; 35 = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3926867/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

